In this episode of *What The Hal?*, Hal Eisner speaks with Andy Lipkis, who started TreePeople in Los Angeles. 

He''s dedicated his life to healing the environment while improving the lives of individuals and communities.  Also on the show is Bryan Rekart, Director of Forestry for TreePeople.

